---
title: Easy Korean Chicken, Corn & Slaw Bowl with Fried Egg & Coriander
description: This sizzling hot Korean chicken from the pan is a delight unparalleled. Delicious marinated chicken and the joy of
simplicity are winners in this dish. A sprinkle of crushed peanuts are the crowning glory of this brilliant twist on the
weeknight dinner.

